posting_body: ['Bedrooms:', '1', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Square Feet:', '547', 'Date Available:', '2022-09-07', 'Address:', '19815 Scriber Lake Road', 'Welcome to Reserve at Lynnwood 55+ Affordable LivingExperience stylish and affordable senior living at the Reserve at Lynnwood.', 'A mixture of urban and suburban, Lynnwood has endless opportunities for shopping and entertainment.', 'The Reserve at Lynnwood is located in the heart of the city just off of Highway 99, within walking distance of major supermarkets, wholesalers, and specialty stores.', 'These new apartments are steps away from retail, dining, and entertainment and have a wide-array of features.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Close to Public Transportation', 'Patio/Balcony', 'Refrigerator', 'Security Camera', 'High Speed Internet', 'Copy and Fax Services', 'On-Site Maintenance', 'Close to Freeway', 'High Ceilings', 'Energy Efficient Appliances', 'Washer/Dryer', 'Free Weights', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing, availability, and specials are subject to change without notice.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
